                            <comment id="228827" author="delbaryg" created="Wed, 30 May 2018 07:33:53 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Hi Shuichi,&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I think 4.12 will not be a LTS version kernel for Linux distribution!&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I did the job for this version because it was the latest vanilla when we wanted to improve Lustre performance.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Yes i agree, your team can rebase theses patches to support 4.14 or 4.15 kernel.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Moreover, it will be nice to wait for some reviewers (to avoid &quot;overwork&quot; on your side).&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
